title: WWE Superstar Set To Return After This Sundays Night Of Champions PPV
content:
King Barrett has wrapped filming on WWE Studios action thriller “Eliminators” in London. He should be back on WWE TV after Night of Champions. Barrett tweeted the following today:
6am wrap pic in North London. Sad it's over, a real privilege to work with such a talented and dedicated crew.  pic.twitter.com/wuhpsH9hEJ— Stu Bennett (@WadeBarrett) September 18, 2015 Share on Facebook Share on Twitter Share on Google Plus About Vin Knight This is a short description in the author block about the author.
